            </div>
        </div>
        
        
        <div id="case-study1" class="row case-study--wrapper" data-number="1">
            <div class="sixteen columns">
                <h3>SUCCESS STORY: <span>A LEADING E-COMMERCE BRAND</span></h3>
                <p>When you need a long-term marketing campaign to remain relevant and engaging, content must be kept fresh. In addition, new goals can be identified and pursued, ranging from boosting brand loyalty to finding new customers. Affectv designed a campaign that would both secure new business opportunities and reduce costs.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>THE AFFECTV APPROACH</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Use innovative methods to prospect new audiences</span></li><li><span>Provide audience insights that can inform future communication strategies</span></li><li><span>Attain a strong cost of sales (COS) figure</span></li>                </ul>
                
                <h4>TARGET AUDIENCE</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>E-commerce shoppers, particularly those browsing, sharing and searching for entertainment-related content.</span></li>                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column cs-insights">
                <h4>OUR INSIGHTS</h4>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs1-1"></div>
                <p>A new audience comprising <strong>parents</strong> was identified for future campaigns (based on sales performance)</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs1-2"></div>
                <p>Audience showed <strong>strong interest</strong> in <strong>television-related content</strong></p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs1-3"></div>
                <p>Audience preferred to share content through social network <strong>Google+</strong> and blogging platform <strong>Wordpress</strong></p>
                
                <!--<p></p>
                
                <p></p>-->
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>OUR RESULTS</h4>
                <p>30% below client COS target</p>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result1-1.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
                <p>12% CPA improvements</p>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result1-2.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="case-study2" class="row case-study--wrapper" data-number="2">
            <div class="sixteen columns">
                <h3>SUCCESS STORY: <span>TOP TIER THEME PARK COMPANY</span></h3>
                <p>An established theme park brand was looking to drive potential customers to their website in order to secure advanced booking for a new exhibition. Affectv launched a highly visible campaign well within the allocated budget.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>THE AFFECTV APPROACH</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Find appropriate audience signals</span></li><li><span>Drive as much traffic to the website as possible</span></li><li><span>Generate awareness about the new exhibition</span></li><li><span>Achieve above within cost constraints</span></li>                </ul>
                
                <h4>TARGET AUDIENCE</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Tourists</span></li><li><span>Young parents</span></li><li><span>Interest in online retail</span></li><li><span>Interest in fashion</span></li><li><span>Interest in youth TV and teen celebrities</span></li><li><span>Interest in gaming</span></li>                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column cs-insights">
                <h4>OUR INSIGHTS</h4>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs2-1"></div>
                <p>Audience majority comprised of <strong>affluent couples</strong></p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs2-2"></div>
                <p>More <strong>females</strong> than males</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs2-3"></div>
                <p>Great interest in<strong>London-related content</strong></p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs2-4"></div>
                <p>Majority likely to be based in <strong>countryside</strong> and not urban settings</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>OUR RESULTS</h4>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result2-1.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
                <p>35% below client CPA targets</p>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result2-2.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="case-study3" class="row case-study--wrapper" data-number="3">
            <div class="sixteen columns">
                <h3>SUCCESS STORY: <span>A TOP-TIER HOTEL GROUP</span></h3>
                <p>Premium brands face the considerable challenge of attracting interest from today’s extremely discerning, advertising-savvy audiences. A top-tier hotel group needed a fresh and effective campaign (with a targeted return of investment of 4000%) that would raise awareness amongst frequent flyers and other travelers within four key European markets.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>THE AFFECTV APPROACH</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Push content and information about the hotel group</span></li><li><span>Find and target an affluent, mature, business-focused audience</span></li><li><span>Achieve an ROI of 4000 percent</span></li>                </ul>
                
                <h4>TARGET AUDIENCE</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Frequenters of upmarket Europe, Middle East and Africa-related events</span></li><li><span>Users of high-income indexed websites</span></li><li><span>Interested in luxury hotels, resorts, airlines, cruises</span></li><li><span>Seek reviews of jewelers and other luxury goods</span></li>                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column cs-insights">
                <h4>OUR INSIGHTS</h4>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs3-1"></div>
                <p>Audience showed strong interest in <strong>books and literature</strong></p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs3-2"></div>
                <p>Majority comprised <strong>affluent businessmen</strong> who do not have children</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs3-3"></div>
                <p>More likely to <strong>browse restaurants and luxury lifestyle guides</strong> than other audiences</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs3-4"></div>
                <p>According to geo-location data, majority were <strong>based in the north of England</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>OUR RESULTS</h4>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result3.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
                <p></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div id="case-study4" class="row case-study--wrapper" data-number="4">
            <div class="sixteen columns">
                <h3>SUCCESS STORY: <span>A LEADING FOOTBALL CLUB</span></h3>
                <p>A prominent Premier League football club approached Affectv to aid hospitality package sales to their fans. The campaign would also have to enhance their profile and drive traffic to the official website. Affectv utilised precise targeting over three strategically chosen match days and came in 75 percent under target cost.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>THE AFFECTV APPROACH</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>Drive content that would spread awareness for the website and VIP match tickets</span></li><li><span>Push messaging to individuals who live close to away match venues or routinely travel to the matches</span></li><li><span>Achieve a cost-per-acquisition figure of £40</span></li>                </ul>
                
                <h4>TARGET AUDIENCE</h4>
                <ul>
                <li><span>People who travel to away matches and have an interest in corporate and individual hospitality events</span></li>                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column cs-insights">
                <h4>OUR INSIGHTS</h4>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs4-1"></div>
                <p>Audience showed strong interest in <strong>real estate, business news and automotive-related content</strong></p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs4-2"></div>
                <p>Majority comprised <strong>affluent young men</strong> who do not have children</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs4-3"></div>
                <p>More likely to browse <strong>football, rugby and holiday content</strong> than other audiences</p>
                
                <div class="cs-insight-icon cs4-4"></div>
                <p>According to geo-location data, majority were based in <strong>small towns outside of London</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="one-third column">
                <h4>OUR RESULTS</h4>
                <p>75% below client cost-per-acquisition target</p>
                <img src="/img/english/cs-result4.png" width="142px" height="142px" />
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>

